column5: Hey all.  Has anyone ever fished in Brampton before?  I have a customer meeting next week out there so I was thinking I might bring some of my gear with me.  Not asking for any honeyhole but any place to fish from shore if there are any.  thanks.  G
theres many little lakes in brampton, heart lake, proffesors lake, lofters lake.... ( large mouth, small mouth, pike)
Take a 20 min. detour and hit Toronto harbour!!! Pike, salmon, missing persons (jk)  Everything in BRAMPTON is getting ready to sleep!!  Drop me a pm.
thanks folks SNAG, when I know the day and time I will contact you if I can seenk it in. CHEERS!
